          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used for contemplation and study and is a Hindu philosophical treatise written from the perspective of Advaita (non-dualism) Vedānta school of philosophy; the work deals with an analysis of knowledge not derived from memory, but through sensory experience of the body.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
